{"tid":1953792,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華為認了：被美國禁令重創、鴻蒙取代不了 Android","createTime":"2020-04-01T11:20:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T04:07:45.000Z","uid":141151,"like":155,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"4e260c3355b8538aaad44f4dd154bb6a177d0294","tid":1953792,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T11:20:43.000Z","msg":"華為認了：被美國禁令重創、鴻蒙取代不了 Android<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://3c.ltn.com.tw/news/39981/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F3c.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2F39981%2F1&d=fPi9TpucIiEDTgLGk%2FOmnb9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=1bdf45d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2F3c.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2F39981%2F1&h=b8d72fe2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://3c.ltn.com.tw/news/39981/1</a><br />\n<br />\n儘管 2019 的營收仍保持 19.1% 的年增速率，華為西歐事業部門負責人兼高級副總裁彭博（Vincent Pang）坦言，受美國貿易禁令影響，不能內建 Google 的服務，已導致華為手機在中國境外的業務受到重擊，同時也讓公司在提升手機銷量時變得「非常困難」（big difficulty）。<br />\n<br />\n彭博也坦言，消費者業務是華為主要的成長動力，但因美國禁令不只影響手機，也連帶讓 Intel 等企業無法提供晶片等關鍵零組件給華為，華為目前的成長動能已被極大地影響。華為安全長 Andy Purdy 也抱怨，美國政府迄今仍不願與華為對話，討論貿易禁令議題。<br />\n<br />\n華為消費者業務首席執行官余承東也在與外媒《Wired》的訪談中回應，盼能得到美國政府的許可重新與 Google 合作，繼續使用 Google 的所有服務，同時把 Play Store 平台作為華為手機的主要內容。<br />\n<br />\n余承東也稱，希望能留用 Android 生態，暗示自家的「鴻蒙」系統和新的 HMS 平台（Huawei Mobile Services）仍不夠成熟，要追上差距，也「需要一到兩年的時間」，余承東說。<br />\n<br />\n華為先前亦曾由美國分公司公共事務副總裁 Joy Tan 出面，坦言於去年 8 月推出的自家手機作業系統「鴻蒙」，想取代 Google Android 的應用生態，仍要數年的時間。儘管華為用戶其實有不少後門管道，可以安裝 Google 的 App 到手機裡，不過除了讓消費者需要額外的操作，Google 也出面警告這些作法可能存在安全疑慮。"},{"pid":"17aa442ebe524ac93f571d1961ae82db5afa0c6e","tid":1953792,"uid":187629,"like":152,"dislike":1,"score":151,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T11:22:37.000Z","msg":"唔係話一出屌打android咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有13億人買驚閪"},{"pid":"ba2739f368b0d524d4a86efcb6604163b608ad3f","tid":1953792,"uid":18912,"like":80,"dislike":0,"score":80,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T11:25:33.000Z","msg":"需要一到兩年的時間<br />\n<br />\n睇得自己咁高.jpg"},{"pid":"003a6bb97e1dbcfa05f1aecf127a95c536da9805","tid":1953792,"uid":13343,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T11:26:34.000Z","msg":"想喺愚人節講出嚟扮假嘢？"},{"pid":"02029f44e47050ff6da3fa06168f60e776ffa6c1","tid":1953792,"uid":146621,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T11:26:52.000Z","msg":"點解唔買ios版權<br />\napple咁奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00f444e0417a3959108b9f9d56e8d595a2d1eb41","tid":1953792,"uid":103230,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T11:26:56.000Z","msg":"坦言於去年 8 月推出的自家手機作業系統「鴻蒙」，想取代 Google Android 的應用生態，仍要數年的時間。<br />\n<br />\n做乜鳩"},{"pid":"4433171e323e3b5df19cf99a3a45d95fb23738d8","tid":1953792,"uid":103230,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"02029f44e47050ff6da3fa06168f60e776ffa6c1","tid":1953792,"uid":146621,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T11:26:52.000Z","msg":"點解唔買ios版權<br />\napple咁奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T11:27:21.000Z","msg":"apple 點會賣野俾人"},{"pid":"790a55b789f4b822834d9997bfe3d4a8ae161cad","tid":1953792,"uid":284699,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"ba2739f368b0d524d4a86efcb6604163b608ad3f","tid":1953792,"uid":18912,"like":80,"dislike":0,"score":80,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T11:25:33.000Z","msg":"需要一到兩年的時間<br />\n<br />\n睇得自己咁高.jpg"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T11:27:25.000Z","msg":"意思係抄得足估計都要一至兩年<br />\n唔係自己開發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30e97e9c6b9878bcfc1780fd33b3f3253cd543c2","tid":1953792,"uid":25169,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"17aa442ebe524ac93f571d1961ae82db5afa0c6e","tid":1953792,"uid":187629,"like":152,"dislike":1,"score":151,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T11:22:37.000Z","msg":"唔係話一出屌打android咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有13億人買驚閪"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T11:27:30.000Z","msg":"13億人:支持華為&mdash;&mdash;此訊息由iPhone 上傳"}